09:27.900 --> 09:29.120
Abang, jangan pergi.

09:30.140 --> 09:31.080
Duduk.

09:32.430 --> 09:33.480
Duduk sini.

09:39.170 --> 09:40.020
Pertama,

09:40.020 --> 09:41.720
